Some usefull scripts to download mangas from http://www.mangareader.net/

--------

current release 0.4 

#######
INSTALL - required only for fetch_news.py
#######
#on debian 6
apt-get install python-pysqlite2 sqlite3
sqlite3 database < database.sql
#edit config.cfg - set all and add your mangas

####
EDIT
####
mangareader.cfg

#####
USAGE
#####
download_manga.py  url
download_chapter.py url

fetch_news.py 

#######
cronjob
#######
0 * * * * /path/to/mangareader/fetch_news.py > /dev/null


